ecord\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"Dr. O'Callaghan\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1858}, {\"ngram\": \"Cork\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1866}, {\"ngram\": \"the hammer title\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1887}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1907}, {\"ngram\": \"their success\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1948}, {\"ngram\": \"a means\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1972}, {\"ngram\": \"his own political agenda\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2008}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The idea of Ireland becoming a host nation came to him when he was in Los Angeles attending the Games and fhe was determined that the Olympic Games would be held in the Irish Free State.\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2023, \"end\": 2030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.999999999994543, \"rank\": 5.364233583960754e-12, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 2081, \"end\": 2092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.384555464708021e-15, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The idea\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"a host nation\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2053}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2112}, {\"ngram\": \"fhe\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2158}, {\"ngram\": \"the Irish Free State\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2196}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was \\\"fairly sure this request will be granted\\\".\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2248, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this request\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2230}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having host