\", \"from\": 4125, \"to\": 4138}, {\"ngram\": \"the content\", \"from\": 4163, \"to\": 4174}, {\"ngram\": \"Preferences\", \"from\": 4182, \"to\": 4193}, {\"ngram\": \"Kieron Wood\", \"from\": 4213, \"to\": 4224}, {\"ngram\": \"his campaign\", \"from\": 4311, \"to\": 4323}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 4350, \"to\": 4367}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If \\u00a3500,000 could be raised from leading Free State citizens, he was \\\"certain that they will be held here\\\".\", \"from\": 4371, \"to\": 4478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4412, \"end\": 4422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Free_State\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5829660324021067e-33, \"text\": \"Free State\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Free_State\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Free_State\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"O'Duffy had raised over \\u00a33,000 in 1931 for the revival of Irish athletics by calling on civil servants, members of the Catholic Church and politicians to donate money.\", \"from\": 4479, \"to\": 4646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4479, \"end\": 4486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eoin_O'Duffy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.039375637528187e-64, \"text\": \"O'Duffy\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eoin_O'Duffy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eoin_O'Duffy\"}, {\"begin\": 4537, \"end\": 4542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9998555175660419, \"rank\": 0.00010901816419044785, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 4598, \"end\": 4613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.999912326676173, \"rank\": 8.768101088673001e-05, \"text\": \"Catholic Church\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the revival\", \"from\": 4522, \"to\": 4533}, {\"ngram\": \"civil servants\", \"from\": 4567, \"to\": 4581}, {\"ngram\": \"members\", \"from\": 4583, \"to\": 4590}, {\"ngram\": \"politicians\", \"from\": 4618, \"to\": 4629}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 4640, \"to\": 4645}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It would have been quite the leap from that to half a million pounds.\", \"from\": 4647, \"to\": 4716, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"quite the leap\", \"from\": 4666, \"to\": 4680}, {\"ngram\": \"half a million pounds\", \"from\": 4694, \"to\": 4715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nonetheless, O'Duffy persisted with newspaper interviews and plans.\", \"from\": 4718, \"to\": 4785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4731, \"end\": 4738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eoin_O'Duffy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.039375637528187e-64, \"text\": \"O'Duffy\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eoin_O'Duffy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eoin_O'Duffy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"newspaper interviews\", \"from\": 4754, \"to\": 4774}, {\"ngram\": \"plans\", \"from\": 4779, \"to\": 4784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Two things will be necessary if we are to hold the Olympic Games here\\\", he noted at one stage, \\\"the conversion of Phoenix Park into a vast Olympic village and the erection of a large imposing stadium near the city\\\".\", \"from\": 4786, \"to\": 5002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Two things\", \"from\": 4787, \"to\": 4797}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 4834, \"to\": 4851}, {\"ngram\": \"one stage\", \"from\": 4871, \"to\": 4880}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"the conversion\", \"from\": 4882, \"to\": 4897}, {\"ngram\": \"Phoenix Park\", \"from\": 4901, \"to\": 4913}, {\"ngram\": \"a vast Olympic village\", \"from\": 4919, \"to\": 4941}, {\"ngram\": \"the erection\", \"from\": 4946, \"to\": 4958}, {\"ngram\": \"a large imposing stadium\", \"from\": 4962, \"to\": 4986}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 4992, \"to\": 5000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The vagueness of the location of the stadium suggests that O'Duffy had not spent much time thinking through the logistics, practicalities and implications of Ireland hosting the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 5003, \"to\": 5195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5062, \"end\": 5069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eoin_O'Duffy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.039375637528187e-64, \"text\": \"O'Duffy\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eoin_O'Duffy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eoin_O'Duffy\"}, {\"begin\": 5161, \"end\": 5168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.999999999994543, \"rank\": 5.364233583960754e-12, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The vagueness\", \"from\": 5003, \"to\": 5016}, {\"ngram\": \"the location\", \"from\": 5020, \"to\": 5032}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium\", \"from\": 5036, \"to\": 5047}, {\"ngram\": \"much time\", \"from\": 5084, \"to\": 5093}, {\"ngram\": \"the logistics\", \"from\": 5111, \"to\": 5124}, {\"ngram\": \"practicalities\", \"from\": 5126, \"to\": 5140}, {\"ngram\": \"implications\", \"from\": 5145, \"to\": 5157}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 5177, \"to\": 5194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He did go as far as \\\"sounding many sportsmen from all countries\\\" while at the 1932 Olympics and described their reaction as enthusiastic.\", \"from\": 5197, \"to\": 5334, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many sportsmen\", \"from\": 5227, \"to\": 5241}, {\"n