]}, {\"sentence\": \"Highlights from the 1932 Olympic Games in Los Angeles Aside from speaking with the IOC boss and some unidentified sportsmen, it is unclear just how far O'Duffy got with the bid for Ireland to host the 1940 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 5482, \"to\": 5703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5524, \"end\": 5535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.384555464708021e-15, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 5566, \"end\": 5569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.257745746201453e-35, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 5635, \"end\": 5642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eoin_O'Duffy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.039375637528187e-64, \"text\": \"O'Duffy\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eoin_O'Duffy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eoin_O'Duffy\"}, {\"begin\": 5664, \"end\": 5671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.999999999994543, \"rank\": 5.364233583960754e-12, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 1932 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 5498, \"to\": 5520}, {\"ngram\": \"the bid\", \"from\": 5651, \"to\": 5658}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1940 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 5679, \"to\": 5701}]}, {\"sentence\": \"O'Duffy's career took several bad turns shortly after he publicised Ireland's Olympic bid.\", \"from